                        preview: "I don\u2019t like Mail.observeAttribute.  This \u201cinitialValue\u201d business feels very specific to unidirectional handling, and doesn\u2019t belong in a shared helper.\r\n\r\nThe latest update to the code makes observing look fairly straightforward:\r\n   var o = new Mutation",
